- [JS API Reference - @tauri-apps/plugin-global-shortcut](https://v2.tauri.app/reference/javascript/global-shortcut/)
- [Window API Reference - Tauri v2](https://v2.tauri.app/reference/javascript/api/namespacewindow/)
- [WebviewWindow API Reference - Tauri v2](https://v2.tauri.app/reference/javascript/api/namespacewebviewwindow/)
- [Core Permissions Reference - Tauri v2](https://v2.tauri.app/reference/acl/core-permissions/)
- [Capabilities Documentation - Tauri v2](https://v2.tauri.app/security/capabilities/)
- [Tauri v2 Global Shortcut Implementation Guide (DEV.to)](https://dev.to/rain9/tauri-8-implementing-global-shortcut-key-function-2336)
